      "acceptanceCriteria": "Linear elastic titanium alloy constitutive model with bilinear plasticity; contact modeled with augmented Lagrangian formulation; validated against published data.",
      "rationale": "The model employs a bilinear isotropic hardening plasticity model for Ti-6Al-4V calibrated from tensile coupon data. Augmented Lagrangian contact at screw-rod and screw-block interfaces captures load transfer appropriately for the quasi-static F1717 protocol."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Model inputs",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 3,
