      "acceptanceCriteria": "Material properties sourced from certified coupon tests; geometry from calibrated CMM measurements; torque preload from calibrated torque wrench records.",
      "rationale": "Ti-6Al-4V elastic modulus (114 GPa), yield strength (880 MPa), and tangent modulus were derived from five tensile coupons per lot. Screw geometry was verified by CMM with ±5 µm tolerance. Torque preload of 4 N·m was applied per protocol and confirmed by calibrated wrench records."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Test samples",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 3,
