      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Quantitative comparison using E/uval metric; all QoIs within 10% relative difference and E/uval < 1.96.",
      "rationale": "For construct stiffness, mean relative difference was 4.2% (E/uval = 0.83). For yield force, mean relative difference was 6.8% (E/uval = 1.41). For force at 40 mm displacement, mean relative difference was 5.1% (E/uval = 1.02). All three QoIs satisfy both acceptance criteria."
    },
