      "rationale": "Construct stiffness, yield force, and force at 40 mm displacement are the three biomechanical endpoints most directly linked to clinical performance of a pedicle screw system under bending. These QoIs are explicitly listed in the COU intended use statement and align with FDA guidance on spinal implant mechanical testing."
